game_description: The game is about Monkeys. you can Jump around and have fun with your friends while playing it. the game has a Gorilla tag based Movement with some extras. there's a shop where you can buy cosmetics with Game-Currency. Everyday you Join the game you get 100 Banans(In-Game_Currency) if you find any bugs you can report them in the Discord! Hope you Enjoy playing Monkeys Place!
